eft: 0px;\">21. Property For Sale and Property for Rent Categories on 5on6.pl</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">If you are listing a property on this Website, your obligations are as follows:</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">Brokers</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">i. You warrant that you possess a valid license from the Real Estate Regulatory Authority , or its equivalent in the republic of poland&nbsp; in which you are advertising;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">ii. If a project is off plan (under construction), you warrant that the project is registered with Real Estate Regulatory Authority ;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">iii. If you are engaging in subleasing activities, you warrant that you possess a license for the activity ;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">iv. If you are engaging in short-term or Holiday Home leasing, you warrant that you possess a license for the activity;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">Developers</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">i. You warrant that you possess a valid license from Real Estate Regulatory Authority, or its equivalent in the republic of poland in which you are advertising;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">ii. If a project is off plan (under construction), you warrant that it is registered with Real Estate Regulatory Authority;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">i. You warrant that you are the Owner/Landlord of the property, or otherwise possess valid authorization to list the property on this Website;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">ii. If you are engaging in short-term or Holiday Home Leasing, you warrant that you possess a license for the activity.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">Tenants</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">i. You warrant that you possess valid, written consent from your Landlord before advertising on this Website, and that you are legally entitled to publish such advertisement.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">All Advertisers</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">i. You may only advertise properties that are currently available for sale or lease. It is at our discretion to remove any listings (advertising fees will not be refunded);</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">ii. You warrant that the advertisement does not contain unlawful language or use of the premises, including:</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">a. defamatory, misleading or deceptive statements;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">b. sharing of a property that exceeds lawful occupancy limits (including, but not limited to, bachelor accommodations and multi-family use);</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">c. sharing of a property between unrelated members of the opposite sex;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">d. sharing of a property in any way that is deemed unlawful;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">e. any other language that promotes illegal or immoral activities under the laws of the republic of poland .</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">If you are listing a property on this Website, your obligations are as follows:</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">i. 5on6.pl advertisements include real properties for sale or rent. AG - Gallado Polska is not a real estate brokerage and the details of the properties available on this Website are provided to us by third party brokers, landlords, owners or developers.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">ii. AG - Gallado Polska does not verify the property listing details provided to us by third parties, and makes no warranties or representations as to their accuracy or completeness.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">iii. You the User of this Website must conduct your own due diligence and must not rely on the details in the advertisements.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">iv. AG - Gallado Polska does verify the&nbsp; license number of all property broker companies prior to allowing them to advertise on the Website.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">22. Motors Category</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">As a user of the Website, you must not offer for sale any type of car, motor vehicle or motorcycle (“Vehicle”) that is:</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">(i) located outside of the Poland, unless you can prove ownership of the Vehicle upon request</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">(ii) that is not immediately for sale;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">(iii) that is not accurately described by the category in which it is advertised;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">(iv) that you are not the owner of, or in all other cases, which you do not have the rights to sell;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">(v) without true and accurate pricing of the Vehicle displayed within the listing.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">We may request that you provide proof of ownership and that the Vehicle is located in the Poland or has been cleared by Polish customs. If you do not provide us with proof within 24 hours of request, we may immediately remove the relevant advertisement/content without further notice and no refund will be made.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">23. Automated data collection </p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">23.1 As a user of the Website, you expressly agree not to use any form of automated data collection such as harvesting bots, robots, spiders, or scrapers, as well as your use of that data.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">23.2 You agree not to use automated data collection methods to obtain the mobile phone numbers and email addresses of our users, and you acknowledge that&nbsp; if you contact our users for the purpose of directing them to your business or website without their express permission to contact them, then you may be prosecuted under Polish laws.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">25. CV Search / Jobs Wanted</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">25.1 AG - Gallado Polska is not responsible for the information posted by the job seekers in the Jobs Wanted section or in their CV\'s. </p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">25.2 The CV Search is a form of head hunting, it allows recruiters to look through the CV\'s in our database. However, some of the applicants may or may not match the job position you are looking to fill. </p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">25.3 Any fees paid are non-refundable once the package is used. </p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">25.4 The duration of the CV Search cannot be extended.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">25.5 By placing a job seeking ad in the Jobs Wanted section, the recruiter will have access to the CV uploaded to the job seeker\'s profile.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">25.6 Once an applicant uploads their CV to their profile, it will be added to our database where recruiters will have access to it for 18 months.</p>',NULL,2,3,1,NULL,NULL,0,0,1,'2019-03-27 08:41:55','2019-06-12 14:20:00'),(21,'pl',21,0,'standard','O nas','o-nas','O nas',NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"http://5on6.pl/\"><span style=\"color: rgb(70, 130, 180); font-size: 10pt;\">5on6.pl</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\"> to pierwszy w Polsce bezpłatny i wielojęzyczny serwis z ogłoszeniami. Powstał w 2019 roku celem stworzenia szerszej platformy do kupowania i sprzedawania nowych i używanych przedmiotów, usług,&nbsp; itp., a także do nawiązywania kontaktów międzynarodowych bez jakichkolwiek barier językowych.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 11pt;\">Każdego roku ponad 15 milionów turystów odwiedza Polskę. W 2017 roku liczba odwiedzających sięgnęła aż 18,7 miliona turystów. W Polsce mieszka ponad milion obcokrajowców.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 11pt;\">Z uwagi na to, że osoby te chętnie kupują towary i usługi z polskiego rynku internetowego, stworzyliśmy wielojęzyczną platformę umożliwiającą wszystkim kupowanie, sprzedawanie, wynajem lub dzierżawę przedmiotów, pojazdów, maszyn, nieruchomości w/z Polski </span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\">bez barier językowych.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 11pt;\">Ponadto międzynarodowi nabywcy (nie zamieszkujący Polski) mogą uzyskać dostęp do polskiego rynku internetowego i dokonywać na nim zakupów czy sprzedaży.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 11pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 11pt;\">5on6.pl - </span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\">Z Polski do reszty świata</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\"><b>FAQS:</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\"><b>1.</b> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\">W jaki sposób opcja wielojęzyczna wpływa na moją sprzedaż?&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\">Wielojęzyczność daje szerszy zakres i większą liczbę potencjalnych klientów. Są&nbsp; to miliony cudzoziemców mieszkających w Polsce i poza nią, którzy chcą kupować Twoje towary i usługi, ale często ze względu na istniejącą barierę językową transakcja nie jest finalizowana. Kupowanie i sprzedawanie towarów i usług nie powinno ograniczać się tylko do jednego kraju.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\"><b>2. </b></span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\">Mam kilka używanych przedmiotów na sprzedaż, najlepiej na eksport, ale mówię tylko po polsku. Jak zatem mogę porozumieć się z potencjalnym nabywcą, który nie mówi po polsku?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\">Ty i kupujący nie musicie mówić tym samym językiem, aby z powodzeniem sfinalizować transakcję.</span><a href=\"http://5on6.pl/\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 85, 204); font-size: 10pt;\">5on6.pl</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\"> oferuje opcję BUY ASSIST, która m.in. pomaga w komunikacji z kupującym/sprzedającym - pamiętaj, aby wybrać opcję BUY ASSIST podczas umieszczania ogłoszenia,&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\"><b>3.</b></span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\"> Jaki jest koszt umieszczenia mojegoh ogłoszenia na</span><a href=\"http://5on6.pl/\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 85, 204); font-size: 10pt;\">5on6.pl</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\">?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\">Zamieszczenie ogłoszenia jest całkowicie darmowe.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\"><b>4.</b> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\">Czy istnieje możliwość promowania mojego ogłoszenia, aby np. było ono widoczne na pierwszej stronie?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\">Istnieje taka jaki i inne możliwości promowania ogłoszeń, a opłaty z tym związane widoczne są podczas dodawania ogłoszenia.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\">Masz jakiekolwiek pytania, skontaktuj się z naszym działem pomocy technicznej: info@5on6.pl.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p><font color=\"#004000\"></font><br></p>',NULL,10,11,1,NULL,NULL,0,0,1,'2019-03-27 11:10:34','2019-08-02 15:56:01'),(22,'en',21,0,'standard','About Us','about-us-en','About Us',NULL,'<p><a href=\"http://5on6.pl/\" target=\"_blank\">5on6.pl</a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13.33px;\"> is the first&nbsp; multilingual free&nbsp; classified ads&nbsp; listing &nbsp; website in poland. Launched in 2019 with the aim of creating a wider platform for buying and selling of new and used items , services and events, etc...&nbsp; between&nbsp; local communities and as well as foreign internationals without language barriers .</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13.33px;\">Every year over 15 million tourists visit&nbsp; Poland. In 2017, poland recorded a ground breaking 18.7 milion tourists.&nbsp; Also not forgetting&nbsp; that&nbsp; over a million foreigners live in Poland.</span></p><p><font color=\"#004000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13.33px;\">In veiw of&nbsp; the fact that