s as a means of payment!</p><p>If you as the seller receive a cheque (generally sent from abroad), where the amount is more than the agreed purchase price, it is more than likely to be attempted fraud. Do not under any circumstances transfer back the overpaid amount to the buyer. The cheque is most likely stolen or a forgery, be careful .</p><p>Unfortunately, it is possible nowadays to falsify the sender\'s address of an email. Scammers use these so-called phishing emails to obtain confidential data (credit card number, passwords etc.) or to represent false facts to a prospective buyer (\"use our trusted payment service\" etc.). 5on6.pl will only contact private customers in connection with an advertisement or a request. As an advertiser/seller, you have provided us either with your credit card number or your account number and sort code to pay for an ad. This data is used solely for the payment of your advertisement! 5on6.pl would never at any stage request this data again – neither by email nor by any other means! As a prospective buyer, you will not receive any emails from 5on6.pl without you first initiating the contact (e.g. email search request, specific request). If, however, you do receive any unsolicited email that appears to be from 5on6.pl , it is undoubtedly a false email.</p><p>5on6.pl will only be involed at some stage of purchase only on special requests from buyers who have already made prior necessary payments in our office in their home country. 5on6.pl does not track who buys&nbsp; from whom. We do not interfere in agreements concerning the sales as undertaken between the buyer and seller. In this respect, 5on6.pl is not able to provide any information concerning the creditworthiness of a buyer ; 5on6.pl do not have access to such information. If, however, you receive an email that appears to be from 5on6.pl and contains statements concerning the creditworthiness of a buyer, this is undoubtedly a false email. All request by buyers who want 5on6.pl to buy or inspect or deliver or ship any vehicle or high end article&nbsp; on their behalf must be strictly triggered over the telephone. If you are in doubt abt any email or any questions please call our help desk right away.<br></p>',NULL,4,5,1,NULL,NULL,0,0,1,'2019-03-29 11:07:42','2019-06-13 08:26:32'),(36,'de',12,0,'standard','Nutzungsbedingungen','nutzungsbedingungen','Nutzungsbedingungen',NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\"><b>Terms of use /&nbsp;Nutzungsbedingungen :</b></p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">WELCOME TO 5ON6.PL!</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">PLEASE READ THIS IMPORTANT LEGAL INFORMATION THAT GOVERNS YOUR USE OF THE 5ON6.PL WEBSITE AND THE SERVICES.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">Last modified: 5 June 2019</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">Introduction</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">&nbsp;AG - Gallado Polska, located in Poland, 11a Ługowka, 05-530 Gora kalwaria tax no:1231252239, regon; <span style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-size: 12px;\">146712204</span> , provides digital advertising and chat services (collectively the “Services”) on the website at <a href=\"http://www.5on6.pl/\">www.5on6.pl</a> and the mobile application of the online platform (collectively the “Website”). Your use of the Website and the Services is governed by these Terms of Service. </p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">These Terms of Service provide you with information about the terms upon which we agree to provide, permit and allow you to access and use the Website. Please print a copy of these Terms of Service and refer to it as you use our Systems and Services. You agree to be bound by these Terms of Service if you continue using the Website. If you do not agree to these Terms of Service, you must immediately refrain from using the Website and the Services.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">We may make changes to the 