nguage that promotes illegal or immoral activities under the laws of the republic of poland .</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">If you are listing a property on this Website, your obligations are as follows:</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">i. 5on6.pl advertisements include real properties for sale or rent. AG - Gallado Polska is not a real estate brokerage and the details of the properties available on this Website are provided to us by third party brokers, landlords, owners or developers.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">ii. AG - Gallado Polska does not verify the property listing details provided to us by third parties, and makes no warranties or representations as to their accuracy or completeness.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">iii. You the User of this Website must conduct your own due diligence and must not rely on the details in the advertisements.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">iv. AG - Gallado Polska does verify the&nbsp; license number of all property broker companies prior to allowing them to advertise on the Website.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">22. Motors Category</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">As a user of the Website, you must not offer for sale any type of car, motor vehicle or motorcycle (“Vehicle”) that is:</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">(i) located outside of the Poland, unless you can prove ownership of the Vehicle upon request</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">(ii) that is not immediately for sale;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">(iii) that is not accurately described by the category in which it is advertised;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">(iv) that you are not the owner of, or in all other cases, which you do not have the rights to sell;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">(v) without true and accurate pricing of the Vehicle displayed within the listing.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">We may request that you provide proof of ownership and that the Vehicle is located in the Poland or has been cleared by Polish customs. If you do not provide us with proof within 24 hours of request, we may immediately remove the relevant advertisement/content without further notice and no refund will be made.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">23. Automated data collection </p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">23.1 As a user of the Website, you expressly agree not to use any form of automated data collection such as harvesting bots, robots, spiders, or scrapers, as well as your use of that data.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">23.2 You agree not to use automated data collection methods to obtain the mobile phone numbers and email addresses of our users, and you acknowledge that&nbsp; if you contact our users for the purpose of directing them to your business or website without their express permission to contact them, then you may be prosecuted under Polish laws.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">25. CV Search / Jobs Wanted</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">25.1 AG - Gallado Polska is not responsible for the information posted by the job seekers in the Jobs Wanted section or in their CV\'s. </p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">25.2 The CV Search is a form of head hunting, it allows recruiters to look through the CV\'s in our database. However, some of the applicants may or may not match the job position you are looking to fill. </p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">25.3 Any fees paid are non-refundable once the package is used. </p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">25.4 The duration of the CV Search cannot be extended.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">25.5 By placing a job seeking ad in the Jobs Wanted section, the recruiter will have access to the CV uploaded to the job seeker\'s profile.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px;\">25.6 Once an applicant uploads their CV to their profile, it will be added to our database where recruiters will have access to it for 18 months.</p>',NULL,2,3,1,NULL,NULL,0,0,1,'2019-03-29 11:09:51','2019-06-12 14:17:31'),(51,'nl',21,0,'standard','Over ons','over-ons','Over ons',NULL,'<p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\">5on6.pl is de eerste gratis en meertalige website met aanbiedingen in Polen.</span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\">Opgericht in 2019 om een breder platform te creëren voor het kopen en verkopen van nieuwe en gebruikte artikelen, diensten, evenementen, enz., En voor het opzetten van internationale contacten zonder enige taalbarrières.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\">Elk jaar bezoeken meer dan 15 miljoen toeristen Polen.</span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\">In 2017 boekte Polen een baanbrekende 18,7 miljoen toeristen.</span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\">Ook niet te vergeten dat meer dan een miljoen buitenlanders in Polen wonen.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\">Voor het feit dat deze mensen ook bereid zijn om goederen en diensten van de Poolse online markt te kopen, hebben we een meertalig platform gecreëerd waarmee iedereen voertuigen, machines, onroerend goed en andere items kan kopen, verkopen, huren of leasen.</span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\">Polen zonder taalbarrières.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\">Bovendien kunnen internationale kopers die momenteel niet in Polen wonen, toegang krijgen tot en kopen op de Poolse internetmarkt.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\">5on6.pl (Van Polen naar de rest van de wereld.)</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\"><b><u>Veelgestelde vragen:</u></b></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\"><b>1.</b> Maar hoe beïnvloedt deze meertalige optie mijn verkoop?</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\">Het geeft u een groter bereik en een groter aantal potentiële klanten.</span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\">Er wonen miljoenen buitenlanders in en buiten Polen die uw goederen en diensten willen kopen, maar dankzij taalbarrières wordt hun toegang geweigerd.</span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\">Het kopen en verkopen van goederen en diensten mag niet worden beperkt tot één taal / land.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\"><b>2.</b> Ik heb verschillende gebruikte artikelen te koop, bij voorkeur voor export, maar ik spreek alleen Pools.</span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\">Hoe kan ik zelfs communiceren met een potentiële koper die geen Pools spreekt?</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-size: 18px;\">U hoeft niet met kopers dezelfde taal te spreken om transacties te voltooien.</span><span style=\"color: